gov.nih.nlm.bioscores.agreement

Class RelaxedHeadMatchAgreement

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.nih.nlm.bioscores.agreement.RelaxedHeadMatchAgreement
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Agreement

    public class RelaxedHeadMatchAgreement
extends java.lang.Object
implements Agreement
    Implementation of one of the precise constructs in Stanford DCoref sieve #9. It can be useful for nominal coreference, but is currently unused.

    Agreement is predicted if the head of the coreferential mention is found in the candidate referent.

    Author:
    Halil Kilicoglu
